{{作品名称|name=''Winter on Fire: Ukraine's Fight for Freedom''|tw=凛冬烈火：烏克蘭自由之戰|cn=凛冬烈火：烏克蘭為自由而戰|equiv-hk=tw}}是一部2015年的[[纪录片|纪录片]]，由葉夫根尼·艾菲尼夫斯基（{{lang|en|Evgeny Afineevsky}}）執導，纪录了[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]在2013年至2014年冬季爆发的[[乌克兰亲欧盟示威运动|亲欧盟示威运动]]，由乌克兰、美国和英国联合制作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tiff.net/festivals/festival15/tiffdocs/winter-on-fire |accessdate=2015-09-21 |title=Winter on Fire: Ukraine's Fight for Freedom (programme note) |publisher=TIFF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150909215630/http://www.tiff.net/festivals/festival15/tiffdocs/winter-on-fire |archivedate=2015-09-09 }}</ref>本片于2015年10月9日在[[Netflix|Netflix]]上释出，在此之前曾数次参加[[电影节|电影节]]的展映。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/thrilling-netflix-documentary-winter-on-fire-ukraines-fight-for-freedom-to-premiere-october-9-20150806 |work=Indiewire |author=Ethan Sapienza |accessdate=2015-09-21 |date=2015-08-06 |title=Thrilling Netflix Documentary 'Winter on Fire: Ukraine's Fight for Freedom' to Premiere October 9 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083446/http://www.indiewire.com/article/thrilling-netflix-documentary-winter-on-fire-ukraines-fight-for-freedom-to-premiere-october-9-20150806 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

因這部記錄片的內容跟2019年香港[[反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動過程|反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動]]的發展相似，有民眾在香港多個地區舉辦放映會公開播放這部記錄片<ref>{{Cite web|title=【逃犯條例】烏克蘭示威紀錄片 網民發起社區放映會|url=https://www.hk01.com/18區新聞/369371/逃犯條例-烏克蘭示威紀錄片-網民發起社區放映會|accessdate=|author=呂諾君|date=2019-08-29|last=|format=|work=|publisher=香港01|language=|archive-date=2020-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200509164129/https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/369371/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E6%9C%83|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=《Winter on fire》街頭放映會遍地開花，烏克蘭抗爭之路對香港有什麼啟示？|url=https://theinitium.com/roundtable/20190829-roundtable-cinematheque-winter-on-fire/|accessdate=|author=|date=2019-08-29|format=|work=|publisher=端傳媒|language=|archive-date=2019-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830223044/https://theinitium.com/roundtable/20190829-roundtable-cinematheque-winter-on-fire/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=反送中》遍地開花放映會 香港人在多區齊放「這部紀錄片」|url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2900404|accessdate=|author=|date=2019-08-30|format=|work=|publisher=自由時報|language=|archive-date=2019-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830223044/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2900404|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

